#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_inputmap.rst:19
msgid ""
"Manages all :ref:`InputEventAction <class_InputEventAction>` which can be"
" created/modified from the project settings menu **Project > Project "
"Settings > Input Map** or in code with :ref:`add_action "
"<class_InputMap_method_add_action>` and :ref:`action_add_event "
"<class_InputMap_method_action_add_event>`. See :ref:`Node._input "
"<class_Node_method__input>`."
msgstr ""
"管理可以从项目设置菜单 **项目>项目设置>输入映射（Project > Project Settings > Input "
"Map）**，或使用带有 :ref:`add_action <class_InputMap_method_add_action>` 和 "
":ref:`action_add_event <class_InputMap_method_action_add_event>` "
"的代码，创建或修改所有 :ref:`InputEventAction <class_InputEventAction>`。参见 "
":ref:`Node._input <class_Node_method__input>`。"

